<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.9">
<l>irukkoṭu nīrcaṅkil koṇṭiṭ ṭeḻilmaṟai yōrvantu niṉṟār</l>
<l>tarukkēlnam picanti niṉṟu tāycolluk koḷḷāy cilanāḷ</l>
<l>tirukkāppu nāṉuṉṉaic cāttat tēcuṭai veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāy</l>
<l>urukkāṭṭu manti viḷakkiṉ ṟoḷikoḷḷa vēṟṟukēṉ vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Eminent Vedic scholars come</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing water in a conch along with the Ṛg Veda and stay.</l>
<l>Don’t be arrogant, [little] Prince!</l>
<l>Standing at the crossroads,</l>
<l rend="indent">adhere to the words of [your] mother for a few [more] days!</l>
<l>You who stands in lustrous Veḷḷaṟai,</l>
<l rend="indent">I will increase the light of the evening lamp that shows [your] form</l>
<l rend="indent">Come so that I [can] adorn you with the holy Kāppu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
